"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-tennis-rafa-nadal-novak-djokovic-paris-2024-b2585728.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The two legends of the men's game might face each other in the second round  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Top seedNovak Djokoviccould face 14-times French Open championRafa Nadalin a blockbuster second-round match in theOlympicsmen's singles after the draw was made at Roland Garros on Thursday.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia's Djokovic, bidding to claim the Olympic gold medal that has eluded him, could have his path blocked by the Spaniard who has reigned supreme on the Parisian clay.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.7933364064947334, \"rank\": 0.2604316497095285, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.949051602169967e-14, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.7430917006504643, \"rank\": 0.34570256938011906, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic, promoted tonumber one seed after the withdrawalof Italy'sJannik Sinnerdue to illness, will face Australia's Matthew Ebden in the opening round atParis 2024.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.98994997798689, \"rank\": 0.008143679997452524, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Ebden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he wins and Nadal beats Hungary's Marton Fucsovics the pair will continue a huge career rivalry which has seen them clash 10 times at the French Open - three in the final, all of which Nadal won.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9786303279912552, \"rank\": 0.021814974549332043, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"score\": 0.9999999956035026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marton Fucsovics\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"h